The problem involves finding a shortest path in a graph, which is a classic topic in computer science and falls under the category of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS). The problem also involves optimization and heuristic solutions, which are common in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of LP-relaxation, simulated annealing, ant colony optimization, and genetic algorithm suggests that the paper may also fall under computational geometry (cs.CG) and discrete mathematics (cs.DM).
